# Cloudflare Pages response headers (applied to the served app/ files).
# Keep this app out of search indexes and add basic hardening for a PII app.
# NOTE: no Content-Security-Policy here on purpose — the app loads React, Babel,
# Tailwind and supabase-js from CDNs at runtime, so a strict CSP would break it.
/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
